Ki-tok-tou5 Choe3-ko E5 Hok8-sai7
Ki-tok-tou5 choe3-ko e5 hok8-sai7 chiu7-si7 saN-thoe3 ki5-to2, che si7 tak8 e5 ki-tok-tou5 long2 tioh8 u7 hun7 e5. Kiam2-chhai2 li2 boe7 hiau2 kong2 to7-li2, chong2-si7 li2 thang ki5-to2; thoe3 pat8-lang5 ki5-to2 si7 li2 e5 koan5-li7, saN-thoe3 ki5-to2 oe7 seng5-chiu7 Siong7-te3 sou2 kau-tai7 lan2 choe3 te7-it toa7 e5 kang.
“Mou5-se to3-tng2 kau3 Ia5-ho5-hoa hia kong2, Ai--ah, chit e5 peh-siN3 hoan7 tang7-choe7, ui7 ka-ki7 choe3 kim e5 Siong7-te3 . TaN Li2 na7 beh sia3-bian2 in e5 choe7------” (Chhut Ai-kip8-ki3 32:31~32). Mou5-se ki5-to2 kau3 chia e5 si5 theng5 tiap8-a2-ku2, chhin-chhiuN7 teh theng3-hau7 Siong7-te3 e5 in3-tap, Hit-si5 i e5 sim-lai7 chin iu-bun7, koh bo5 thiaN tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 in3-tap, sou2-i2 i e5 sim kan-khou2 kau3-kek8. Chong2-si7 i thiaN3 peh-siN3 e5 sim chin chhiat, chiu7 koh soa3-chiap ki5-to2 kong2: “Na7 m7, kiu5 Li2 tui3 Li2 sou2 sia2 e5 chheh, chhat-khi3 goa2 e5 mia5”.
Siong7-te3 e5 lou5-pok8 ui7-tioh8 I e5 peh-siN3 ki5-to2 kau3 chiah ki5-biau7! Ti7 i sim-lai7 e5 tang7-taN3 koh si7 hiah-nih tang7; i teh thoe3 in ki5-kiu5 e5 si5, i sim-lai7 e5 thong3-khou2 si7 lan2 boe7 thang liau2-kai2 e5, i e5 thiaN3 sit8-chai7 chin chhim.
Kiam2 bat u7 lang5 tu2-tioh8 chit khoan2 keng-giam7? Na7 kap chit ui7 ui2-tai7 tai7-to2 e5 lang5 ------Mou5-se, saN pi2-kau3, lan2 e5 tai7-to2 sit8-chai7 bo5 khui3-lat8. I2-sek-liat8 peh-siN3 na7 oe7 tit-kiu3, i kam-goan7 tui3 oah8-mia7 chheh chhat-khi3 i e5 mia5, eng2-oan2 kap Siong7-te3 keh-li7. M7-na7 Mou5-se u7 chit khoan2 keng-giam7, ti7 Sin-iok Seng3-keng sou2 ki3-chai3, Po2-lo5 ia7 u7 chit khoan2 e5 keng-giam7. Po2-lo5 kong2: “Goa2 tiam3-ti7 Ki-tok kong2-oe7 chin-sit8 bo5 peh8-chhat8, goa2 e5 liong5-sim ti7 Seng3 Sin5 kap goa2 saN-kap choe3 kan-cheng3, goa2 u7 toa7 iu-bun7, thong3-sim bo5 soah. In-ui7 goa2 ui7-tioh8 goa2 e5 hiaN-ti7, goa2 e5 kut-jiok8 e5 chi3-chhin, chiu7 na2 pun2-sin siu7 chiu3-chou2 li7-khui Ki-tok ia7 kam-goan7” (Lo5-ma2 9:1~3).
ChaiN2-iuN7 teh bio5-sia2 Po2-lo5 e5 sim-keng2 ah! Lan2 siuN7 i si7 chit8 e5 sim-lai7 put-si5 chhiong-moa2 khoai3-lok8, koh khou2-khng3 pat8-lang5 tioh8 hoaN-hi2 khoai3-lok8 e5 lang5 . Chong2-si7 ti7 chia kong2 i u7 toa7 iu-bun7, thong3-sim bo5-soah, chit-e5 tang7-taN3 mi5-jit8 tak8 si5-khek long2 teh teh i, hou7 i kan-khou2 kau3-kek8, chiu7-si7 ui7-tioh8 i e5 hiaN-ti7, kut-jiok8 e5 chi3-chhin, chiu7 pun2-sin siu7 chiu3-chou2 eng2-oan2 li7-khui Ki-tok ia7 kam-goan7.
Po2-lo5 kap Mou5-se long2 u7 kang7 chit8 iuN7 e5 sim, chiu7-si7 in sit8-chai7 thiaN3 in e5 tong5-pau I2-sek-liat8 lang5 , I chim-chiok kho2-lu7 liau2, chi2-u7 ui7-tioh8 Iu5-thai3 lang5 ki5-to2, eng7 toa7 khui3-lat8, bo5 theng5 ui7-tioh8 in tai7-to2, i e5 sim-lai7 chiah oe7 khin-sang.
Ki3-jian5 u7 chit khoan2 tai7-to2 e5 bou5-iuN7, chiu7-si7 tui3 iu-siong kau3-kek8 e5 sim-sin5 sou2 chhut e5 ki5-to2, chiu7 chai lan2 e5 ki5-to2 m7 chiaN5 ki5-to2, sit8-chai7 thang pi-siong. Goan7 Siong7-te3 pang-chan7 lan2, hou7 lan2 ui7-tioh8 pat8-lang5 the2-thiap hit e5 tang7-taN3, eng7 moa2-moa2 u7 khui3-lat8 e5 tai7-to2 lai5 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3 .
Ki5-to2 E5 Tiau5-kiann7
Tai7-seng, lan2 tioh8 hah8 ti7 ki5-to2 e5 tiau5-kiaN7, chiu7-si7 lan2 kap Siong7-te3 e5 koan-he7 tioh8 u7 chheng-chho2 , na7 bo5, ki5-to2 bo5 lou7-eng7. Seng3-keng kong2: “Goa2 na7 sim-lai7 chu3-tiong7 choe7-ok, Chu2 tek-khak bo5 beh thiaN.” Lan2 beh ho2-taN2 ki5-to2, tioh8 tu5-khi3 sou2 u7 e5 choe7-ok, li7-khui kiN3-na7 oe7 hou7 Seng3 Sin5 iu-bun7, hou7 I bo5 hoaN-hi2 e5 tai7-chi3. An2-ni, chiah oe7 hah8 ti7 ki5-to2 e5 tiau5-kiaN7, chiah oe7 thang choe3 chit8-e5 thoe3 lang5 ki5-to2 e5 lang5 , u7-hun7 ti7 Ki-tok-tou5 choe3-ko e5 hok8-sai7.
Tai7-to2 E5 I3-gi7
Tai7-to2 chiu7-si7 ui7-tioh8 lan2 ka-ki7 e5 bun7-toe5 kap su-iau3 i2-goa7 e5 tai7-chi3 ki5-to2. Ti7 leng5 e5 lai7-bin7 kap Ia5-sou Ki-tok saN-kap beh hou7 lang5 tit-tioh8 hok-khi3 e5 kang-chok, hou7 lan2 tam-tng pat8-lang5 leng5-hun5 seng-san2 e5 kan-khou2, hou7 Seng3 Sin5 chiau3 Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3, thong-ke3 lan2 ki5-to2.
Seng3-keng sou2 ki3-chai3 e5 ki5-to2, toa7 pou7-hun7 long2 si7 ui7-tioh8 pat8-lang5 e5 ki5-to2. Mou5-se kap Po2-lo5 chi2-u7 ui7-tioh8 I2-sek-liat8 lang5 ki5-to2. Chu2 IA5-sou pun2-sin chin han2-tit ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 e5 su-iau3 ki5-to2. I e5 tang7-taN3 chiu7-si7 hiah-e5 put-si5 oe-khoeh ti7 I sin-piN e5 cheng3-lang5 . Tai7-to2 chiu7-si7 thoe3 pat8-lang5 ki5-kiu5.
Tai7-to2 iau2 u7 chit8-e5 i3-gi7, chiu7-si7 lan2 tioh8 eng7 Ia5-sou e5 sim choe3 sim kap I saN-kap tam-tng I sim-lai7 e5 tang7-taN3, beh chai I e5 ke3-ek8 kap I sou2 beh choe3 e5 kang, ui7-tioh8 chiah-e5 su7 lai5 ki5-to2. Lan2 siong5-siong5 bo5 siuN7-tioh8 chit-hang7 su7, ti3-kau3 lan2 ki5-to2 e5 loe7-iong5 long2-si7 chip8-tiong ti7 lan2 pun2-sin. Lan2 e5 su-iau3 kap i3-ai3 chiam3 lan2 ki5-to2 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 pou7-hun7. Lan2 tioh8 chhiau-oat8 chit-hang7. Lan2 tioh8 ki5-to2 kau3 ka-ki7 it-chhe3 e5 tai7-chi3 long2 siat-hoat liau2, chiah oe7 thang thoe3 pat8-lang5 ki5-to2. Siong7-te3 ai3 beh chiaN5 e5 su7 si7 sim2-mih8? I tui3 chit-hang7 kang-chok a2-si7 hit-hang7 kang-chok e5 ke3-ek8 chaiN2-iuN7? Lan2 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 chiah oe7 ui7-tioh8 Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 li7-ek gau5 hok8-sai7 I koh eng5-kng I e5 mia5? Chiah-e5 long2 si7 lan2 eng-kai tioh8 mng7 e5 bun7-toe5, sou2-i2 lan2 tioh8 ti7 I e5 bin7-cheng5 theng3-hau7, kau3 I chiong sim-lai7 e5 tang7-taN3 tui3 lan2 hian2-beng5, lan2 chiah oe7 the2-thiap Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 sim, ui7-tioh8 chiah-e5 su7 ki5-to2, hou7 I sou2 beh choe3 e5 kang oe7 oan5-seng5.
An2-ni, lan2 ia7 tioh8 beng5-pek8 Seng3 Sin5 e5 koan5-leng5 kap pang-chan7, in-ui7 chi2-u7 I chai-iaN2 Siong7-te3 e5 sim-i3. Hang5-hok8 I e5 lang5 , I chiu7 chi2-si7, in2-chhoa7, koh chio3 kng in e5 lou7, hou7 in e5 ki5-to2 tek-khak tat8-tioh8 bok8-tek. Lan2 oan5-choan5 sin3-kho3 I, chiong pun2-sin oan5-choan5 kau hou7 I, I chiu7 in2-chhoa7 lan2 chiau3 Siong7-te3 e5 ke3-ek8 kap bok8-tek lai5 ki5-to2. Sou2-i2 kap Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok saN-kap ki5-to2, che hoaN-hi2 kap hok-khi3 si7 joa7-toa7! Ui7-tioh8 lan2 ka-ki7 ki5-to2 sou2 tit e5 khoai3-lok8, kap che oan5-choan5 bo5-kang7.
Te7-it Khun3-lan5 E5 Kang-chok
Tai7-to2 si7 Ki-tok-tou5 choe3-ko e5 hok8-sai7, ia7 si7 te7-it khun3-lan5 e5 kang-chok. Toa7 pou7-hun7 e5 lang5 long2 liah8-choe3 ki5-to2 si7 chin khoai3 choe3 e5 tai7-chi3, long2 bo5 tam7-poh8-a2 khun3-lan5. Che si7 in-ui7 in long2 m7 chai tai7-to2 e5 kang-chok. In e5 ki5-to2 long2-si7 ui7 in pun2-sin, ka-chok8 kap ko3-jin5 e5 li7-ek choe3 tiong-sim, ia7 chi2-u7 chit8-nng7-pai2 bat ui7-tioh8 tim5-lun5 e5 goa7-pang-lang5 ki5-to2. In u7-si5 eng7 gou7 hun, chap8 hun-cheng e5 si5-kan lai5 ki5-to2. Chong2-si7 in long2 m7-bat siuN7, tak8-jit8 tioh8 poah it-teng7 e5 si5-kan lai5 ki5-to2, a2-si7 eng7 kui poaN3-mi5 e5 si5-kan ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 theng3-hau7 kap I kau-poe5. In ki5-to2 e5 seng-oah8, bo5 eng2-kiu2-seng3, in khoaN3 ki5-to2 choe3 bo5 sim2-mih8 iau3-kin2; na7 u7 tai7-chi3 chiu7 khi3 choe3, long2 bo5 teh siuN7 beh ki5-to2. Chit khoan2 lang5 e5 seng-oah8 long2 boe7 eng2-hiong2 tioh8 Sat-tan3 e5 kak-tou7, sou2-i2 in khoaN3 ki5-to2 si7 chin kan2-tan e5 su7.
Chong2-si7 u7-hun7 ti7 tai7-to2 kang-chok e5 Ki-tok-tou5 it-teng7 oe7 tu2-tioh8 bo5 kang7-khoan2 e5 keng-giam7. Sat-tan3 beh chin7 i sou2-u7 e5 khui3-lat8, kap long2-chong2 e5 hoat-tou7 lai5 chou2-tong3, in it-teng7 oe7 sit8-chai7 the2-giam7 tioh8 Sat-tan3 ti7 hian7-tiuN5 teh ti2-tek8. I2-au7 ia7 oe7 sit-chi3, chit8-pai2 koh chit8-pai2, siuN7 beh pang3-sak che tai7-to2 e5 kang-chok. Bok8-koai3 Chu2 Ia5-sou eng7 poaN3-mi5 u7 peng5-iu2 lai5 e5 phi3-ju7 ka3-si7 lan2. Eng7 bo5 boe7 eng7-tit e5 sim-cheng5 pek-chhiat kiu5, che si7 beh hou7 lan2 e5 ki5-to2 seng5-kong te7-it toa7 e5 in-sou3. Lan2 ki5-to2 chit8 e5 si5, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 eng3-un2 iau2-be7 kau3, lan2 chiu7 sit-chi3 bo5 koh ki5-to2. An2-ni chiu7-si7 Sat-tan3 eng7 i te7-it u7 koan5-hau7 e5 bu2-khi3 lai5 tui3-hu3 lan2, pho3-hoai7 lan2 e5 koat-i3, bo5 choe3 tai7-to2 e5 lang5 .
Sou2 u7 e5 hong-hoat long2 sit-pai7, i iau2 beh hou7 lan2 u7 hun7 ti7 choe7-choe7 khoan2 e5 kang-chok. Sat-tan3 leng5-khou2 ai3 lan2 khi3 bo5-eng5 choe3 kang, bo5 ai3 lan2 u7 si5-kan ki5-to2. In-ui7 i chai-iaN2 bo5 ki5-to2 e5 kang-chok it-teng7 bo5 leng5-lek8, koh bo5 hau7-ko2; sou2-i2 i na7 oe7 hou7 lan2 bo5-eng5 kau3 bo5 si5-kan thang ki5-to2, i chiu7 i2-keng tat8 i e5 bok8-tek.
HiaN-ti7 chi2-be7, goa2 beh khng3 li2 thiat-ti2 kam3-chhat li2 e5 seng-oah8, khoaN3 li2 sou2 teh choe3 e5, si7 sit8-chai7 iau3-kin2 e5 su7 mah? Phah-sng3 li2 kan-ta u7-hun7 ti7 kau3-hoe7 tak8-khoan2 e5 oah8-tang7, ti3-kau3 bo5 si5-kan thang ki5-to2. Goa2 beh kiu5 li2, ti7 iau2-be7 siuN-ban7 i2-cheng5, tioh8 chhiau5 hou7 i si3-chiaN3, tu5-khi3 hiah-e5 m7-si7 ki-pun2-tek e5, bian2 ti3-kau3 ka-ki7 siuN bo5-eng5. Chong2-si7 tek-khak tioh8 siat-hoat hou7 li2 u7 si5-kan kap Siong7-te3 kau-poe5, an2-ni, chiu7 li2 ti7 chit8 geh8-jit8 e5 tiong-kan, sou2 oan5-seng5 e5 kang, pi2 chit8 ni5 khah choe7.
“Ki-tok Ia5-sou e5 lou5-pok8, I2-pa-hut, chiu7-si7 lin2 hia e5 lang5 , chheng2-an lin2; i ti7 ki5-to2 e5 tiong-kan siong5 siong5 ui7-tioh8 lin2 chhut-lat8” (Ko-lo5-se 4:12). SiaN2-su7 tioh8 chhut-lat8? Lan2 toa7 pou7-hun7 e5 lang5 ti7 ki5-to2 e5 si5 kan-tan chiong lan2 e5 su-iau3 ka7 Siong7-te3 kong2-beng5, siong-sin3 I beh ka7 lan2 chiaN5, i2-au7 chiu7 m7-bat koh siuN7 chiah-e5 su7. Chong2-si7 I2-pa-hut m7 si7 an2-ni; i chiah si7 chit8-e5 chin-chiaN3 teh tai7-to2 e5 lang5 , in-ui7 i beng5-pek8 tai7-to2 si7 khun3-lan5 e5 kang-chok. Po2-lo5 kong2, I2-pa-hut thoe3 pat8-lang5 ki5-to2 si7 chin chhut-lat8, pek-chhiat tioh8-boa5 teh ki5-to2, a2-si7 kong2, lou2-lek8 teh cheng-chian3. Li2 kiam2 chai-iaN2 ki5-to2 si7 khou2-chian3 mah?
“Ia5-sou khou2-thang3 kau3 kek8, ki5-to2 na2 pek-chhiat; I e5 koaN7 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 toa7 tiam2 huih tih loh8 toe7” (Lou7-ka 22:44). Siong7-te3 e5 KiaN2 bat an2-ni ki5-to2, in-ui7 ki5-to2 si7 I sou2 tioh8 choe3, te7-it khun3-lan5 e5 kang. Tong-jian5 ki5-to2 si7 kap Siong7-te3 kau-poe5, si5-siong5 hou7 lan2 tit-tioh8 hoaN-hi2 khoai3-lok8 kap I e5 chiok-hok; chong2-si7 tu2-tioh8 tui3-tek8, ki5-to2 chiu7 chiaN5-choe3 kau-chian3. Chit khoan2 e5 ki5-to2 tau3-ti2 lan2 jim7-bat joa7-choe7?
Seng3-keng kong2: “Chu2 Ia5-sou khou2-thang3 kau3 kek8”, I khai-si2 ki5-to2 bo5 ku2 chiu7 ki5-to2 na2 pek-chhiat. Chit-e5 kang-chok hiah khun3-lan5, khou2-thang3 hiah toa7, tang7-taN3 hiah tang7, ap-lek8 hiah thang-kiaN, I e5 koaN7 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 toa7-tiam2 huih tih loh8 toe7. Kin2-tiuN kau3 an2-ni; kau-chian3 kau3 hiah nih thang kiaN! An2-ni, lan2 tai7-to2 e5 seng-oah8 sit8-chai7 thai3 khui-khiam3! Lan2 sit8-chai7 bo5 sim2-mih8 chai Siong7-te3 e5 KiaN2 sou2 taN e5 tang7-taN3.
“Koh Seng3 Sin5 ia7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni hu5-chhi5 lan2 e5 nng2-chiaN2; in-ui7 lan2 m7 chai-iaN2 tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 ki5-to2 chiau3 sou2 eng-kai e5; tok8-tok8 Seng3 Sin5 ka-ki7 eng7 boe7 kong2-chhut e5 thou2-khui3 thoe3 lan2 kiu5” (Lo5-ma2 8:26). Ti7 chia lan2 khoaN3-tioh8 Seng3 Sin5 kap ki5-to2 e5 koan-he7; I ia7 teh ki5-to2, chhin-chhiuN7 Ia5-sou bat ki5-to2. An2-ni, Seng3 Sin5 teh thoe3 lan2 ki5-to2 kau3 sim2-mih8 khoan2? Seng3-keng kong2: “Thou2-khui3 thoe3 lan2 kiu5”. Che si7 beh hou7 lan2 chai, hit-e5 kin2-tiuN kap thong3-khou2. Seng3 Sin5 e5 thou2-khui3 si7 boe7 kong2-chhut e5, in-ui7 ti7 se3-kan bo5 chit8-hang7 oe7 thang oan5-choan5 piau2-tat8 Seng3 Sin5 thoe3 lan2 ki5-to2 pek-chhiat kau3 chaiN2-iuN7, che thou2-khui3 si7 kong2 boe7 chhut e5.
Te7-it U7 Hau7-ko2 E5 Bu2-khi3
Tai7-to2 si7 Ki-tok-tou5 te7-it u7 hau7-ko2 e5 bu2-khi3, bo5 chit8 hang7 oe7 ti2-tng ki5-to2 e5 leng5-lek8; chiu7-si7 sou2-i7 e5 hong-hoat long2 sit-hau7, oa2-kho3 ki5-to2 oe7 oan5-seng5 choe7-choe7 su7. Chong2-si7 ki5-koai3 e5 tai7-chi3, chiu7-si7 chi2-u7 ki5-to2 chiah choe3 oe7 kau3 e5 su7, lan2 hoan2-tng2 eng7 pat8-khoan2 e5 se3-lek8 beh oan5-seng5. Siong7-te3 i2-keng chiong che te7-it u7 hau7-ko2 e5 bu2-khi3 siuN2-su3 lan2, ai3 lan2 gau5 eng7 i. Lan2 na7 khng3 he7 teh m7 eng7, beh eng7 siok8 hiat-khi3 e5 hoat-tou7 choe3 chhiau chu7-jian5 e5 kang, I tek-khak chin sit-bang7.
Bou7-tek8 thau5 chit8-pai2 khi3 Sou-kek-lan5 e5 Ai3-teng-po2 thoan5 to7-li2 e5 si5, ti7 bo5 kui2-jit8 e5 tiong-kan, choan5 siaN5 in-ui7 i e5 to7-li2 u7 chhim-tou7, chiu7 long2 han2 khi2-lai5; m7-na7 an2-ni, Sou-kek-lan5 sou2-u7 e5 siaN5-chhi7 ia7 long2 u7 hun3-heng; bo5-ku2, lang5 chiu7 tui3 choan5-kok che7 he2-chhia lai5 kau3 i teh thoan5 to7-li2 e5 sou2-chai7 hu3 chu7-hoe7, in-ui7 lang5 -lang5 koan-sim teh him-bou7 to7-li2; che su7 chaiN2-iuN7 oe7 an2-ni? Goan5-lai5 chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 eng3-un2 tui3 ke3-khi3 kui2 na7 geh8-jit8 i2-lai5 chit8 lang5 tak8-jit8 choe7-choe7 pai2 e5 tai7-to2, hou7 cheng3-lang5 hut-jian5-kan chin ti3-i3 siok8-leng5 e5 su7. Kiat-ko2, chin-choe7 lang5 hoan2-hoe2 sin3 Chu2 Ia5-sou. Hit-pai2 ti7 Sou-kek-lan5, Seng3 Sin5 toa7 choe3-kang. TaN kau3 ti7 kin-a2-jit8, ti7 Eng-kok choan5-kok kau3-hoe7 e5 chi2-to7-chia2, a2-si7 ui7-tioh8 Chu2 bat oan5-seng5 toa7-su7 e5 sin3-tou5, toa7 pou7-hun7 long2 si7 ti7 Bou7-tek e5 chu7-hoe7 hoan2-hoe2 tit-kiu3 e5 lang5 . Hit e5 pi3-koat, lang5 -lang5 long2 chai-iaN2 si7 tai7-to2 e5 kiat-ko2.
“Gi7-lang5 e5 ki5-to2, i e5 lek8-liong7 u7 toa7 kong-hau7” (Nga2-kok 5:16). Che si7 Siong7-te3 tui3 tai7-to2 e5 kou2-ke3. Seng3-keng chiu7 eng7 sian-ti I2-li7-a e5 kang-chok choe3 phi3-ju7 lai5 soat-beng5. I chiau3 Siong7-te3 sou2 chi2-teng7 e5 hong-hoat, khi3 choe3 tai7-chi3, che si7 chin ki5-biau7 e5 su7. Goa2 siuN7 i ti7 seng-khu put-si5 u7 toa3 thian-kok e5 so2-si5, i eng7 chit-ki so2-si5 chiong thiN koaiN-bat8, chiu7 bo5 koh loh8-hou7. SaN ni5 poaN3 i2-au7, i koh theh8 hit-ki so2-si5 khui-thiN, hiu7 loh8 toa7-hou7. I gau5 eng7 toa7 leng5-lek8 e5 bu2-khi3------tai7-to2 hou7 tai7-chi3 oe7 chiaN5.
“Tui3 an2-ni Pi2-tek lau5 ti7 kaN-nih8; tok8-tok8 kau3-hoe7 thoe3 i chhiat-chhiat kiu5 Siong7-te3 ” (Su3-tou5 Heng7-toan7 12:5). Pi2-tek hou7 lang5 liah8 khi3 koaiN kaN, che si7 lang5 e5 khui3-lat8. Na7-si7 Seng3-keng koh kong2: “Tok8-tok8 kau3-hoe7 thoe3 i chhiat-chhiat kiu5 Siong7-te3 ”. Chhou-tai7 kau3-hoe7 chai-iaN2 tai7-to2 e5 leng5-lek8, kiat-ko2 Pi2-tek tit-tioh8 chu7-iu5. In-ui7 Siong7-te3 eng3-un2 kau3-hoe7 ki5-kiu5 e5 siaN, chhe thiN-sai3 lai5 kiu3 Pi2-tek chhut-kaN.
