Tng-si5 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 chhut-goa7, khi3 ti7 chhit, poeh chap8 li2 goa7 e5 sou2-chai7, goa2 long2 m7-chai i sim-lai7 e5 tai7-chi3. U7 chit8-jit8 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 chiah8 tiong-tau3 pa2, ti7 e7-poe-si5 tit-tioh8 kam2-tong7 chin ai3 i e5 kiaN2 hoan2-hoe2 tit-kiu3. Kam2-kak tioh8 an2-ni, i chiu7 jip8-khi3 pang5-keng, so2 mng5, thoe3 goa2 ki5-to2, koat-i3 na7 bo5 tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 eng3-un2, chiu7 bo5 beh li7-khui hia. Goa2 e5 lau7-bu2, chit8-tiam2-cheng koh chit8-tiam2-cheng thoe3 goa2 pek-chhiat ki5-to2 kau3 boe7 thang koh chai3 ki5-to2; kau3 i tit-tioh8 kam2-tong7, tioh8 o-lo2 Siong7-te3 , in-ui7 Seng3 Sin5 u7 chi2-si7 i kong2, tai7-chi3 i2-keng chiaN5 lah------chiu7-si7 i chit e5 kiaN2 u7 hoan2-hoe2. Keng-ke3 nng7 le2-pai3 au7 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 tng2-lai5 kau3 chhu3, goa2 chiu7 sui5-si5 chiong goa2 i2-keng hoan2-hoe2 sin3 Chu2 e5 ho2 siau-sit beh ka7 i kong2. Goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 chiong goa2 lam2 tiau5 tai7-seng kong2, KiaN2 ah, goa2 chai, li2 sou2 beh ka7 goa2 kong2 e5 ho2 siau-sit, goa2 i2-keng hoaN-hi2 nng7 le2-pai3 ku2 teh theng3-hau7 lah.
